h2-open-web-paywalls-p61caa68e.translation:
这样，一旦支付成功并更新了访问权限，订阅几乎会立即在应用中激活。

```csharp showLineNumbers title="Unity"
Adapty.OpenWebPaywall(
    product,
    (error) =>
    {
        if (error != null)
        {
            Debug.LogError($"Failed to open web paywall: {error.Message}");
        }
        else
        {
            Debug.Log("Web paywall opened successfully");
        }
    }
);
```

h2-open-web-paywalls-in-an-in-app-browse.translation:
```csharp showLineNumbers title="Unity"
Adapty.OpenWebPaywall(
    product,
    AdaptyWebPresentation.InAppBrowser, // default — ExternalBrowser
    (error) =>
    {
        if (error != null)
        {
            Debug.LogError($"Failed to open web paywall: {error.Message}");
        }
        else
        {
            Debug.Log("Web paywall opened successfully");
        }
    }
);
```
